thread.title: James Smith, SVP, OceanFirst Bank
thread.title_full: American Executive Centers reviewed by James Smith, SVP, OceanFirst Bank

author: James Smith, SVP, OceanFirst Bank
title: James Smith, SVP, OceanFirst Bank
text:
Location is exceptional with ample parking. The interior layout of the space is comfortable. The staff has always conducted themselves with upmost professionalism and courtesy.
My team at Ocean First has enjoyed the experience and we would highly recommend this space to anyone.
